       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID. NOTICE1.
      * CHARGE-CHANGE NOTICE WINDOW (MO-0 COMMENT/STYLE EDIT)
       ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
       DATA DIVISION.
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
       01  WS-NOTICE-DAYS            PIC 9(4) VALUE ZERO.
       01  WS-OK                     PIC X(1) VALUE 'N'.
       PROCEDURE DIVISION.
       1000-MAIN.
           ACCEPT WS-NOTICE-DAYS
           PERFORM 2000-CHK
           DISPLAY 'OK= ' WS-OK
           STOP RUN.
       2000-CHK.
           IF WS-NOTICE-DAYS >= 30
              MOVE 'Y' TO WS-OK
           END-IF.
